Class Project3

java.lang.Object
Project3
public class Project3
extends java.lang.Object
This class is in charge of reading a .txt file and creating a Clock object out of the content of the file Then adding those objects as nodes into two lists, UnsortedClockList and SortedClockList which both inherets from a super class called ClockList Then creating a GUI to represent both the sorted and unsorted lists
Author:
Bola Gadalla
